    "bookShortLabel": "7下",
    "bookOrder": 221,
    "summary": "回望中国女足逆转夺冠，理解荣誉背后的长期奋斗。"
  },
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s1",
      "text": "The 2022 Women’s Asian Cup final was a difficult match.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p1",
      "tr": "2022年女足亚洲杯决赛是一场艰难的比赛。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "Women’s Asian Cup final 是主语；was 是系动词；difficult match 是表语。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/sETiRCaQtohpjJPqENdSYf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s2",
      "text": "At half-time, the Chinese team was losing 2–0.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p1",
      "tr": "半场结束时，中国队以0-2落后。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "At half-time 是时间状语；was losing 是过去进行时。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/TabxCPY39rYAVSGsH6Ss6Q.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s3",
      "text": "Even worse, the team’s best player hurt her foot badly.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p1",
      "tr": "更糟糕的是，队中最好的球员脚部严重受伤。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "Even worse 是插入语；hurt 是过去式；badly 是副词修饰动词。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ENeBdr5XMkKdCYjuGPr4dB.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s4",
      "text": "But she paid no attention to the pain and continued to play.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p1",
      "tr": "但她没有在意疼痛，继续比赛。",
      "g": "并列复合句",
      "d": "pay attention to 意为“注意”；continued to play 意为“继续做某事”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/wR9oYfs4oxHnyhx3DE8bBZ.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s5",
      "text": "Her brave actions encouraged the whole team.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p1",
      "tr": "她的勇敢行为鼓舞了全队。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "brave actions 是主语；encouraged 是谓语动词。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/Jjt9xCaRFgpbPT9dqhatdA.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s6",
      "text": "None of the players lost heart.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p1",
      "tr": "没有一名球员丧失信心。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "None of... 意为“没有人...”；lost heart 意为“丧失信心/灰心”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/6W85vuLwPkohirb5FfUbM4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s7",
      "text": "They fought on and scored three goals in the last 25 minutes.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p1",
      "tr": "她们继续战斗，并在最后25分钟内攻入三球。",
      "g": "并列复合句",
      "d": "fought on 意为“继续战斗”；scored 意为“得分/进球”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/iFXRjrnrFz9X3ouMD7CDJh.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s8",
      "text": "The amazing victory led people to look back at the team’s early days.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p2",
      "tr": "这场惊人的胜利让人们回想起球队早期的日子。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语 + 宾语补足语",
      "d": "led sb. to do sth. 意为“引导某人做某事”；look back at 意为“回顾”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/nCQy2ngCY8LuvAu9Z5QubA.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s9",
      "text": "Those were years of great challenges.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p2",
      "tr": "那是充满巨大挑战的岁月。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "Those 是代词作主语；challenges 意为“挑战”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/tQAyJy49fFEVDmczzdSPKB.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s10",
      "text": "In 1986, the China women’s football team played its first international match.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p2",
      "tr": "1986年，中国女足参加了首场国际比赛。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "international match 意为“国际比赛”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/uTH4gjAu5cJ2SLwemVVFQm.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s11",
      "text": "Both of the teams played hard, but China lost 2–1 to the USA.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p2",
      "tr": "两支球队都打得很努力，但中国队以1-2负于美国队。",
      "g": "并列复合句",
      "d": "Both of... 意为“两者都...”；lost to... 意为“输给...”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/WXcu4ptqF8f557Chmsdcrd.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s12",
      "text": "However, the players never gave up.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p2",
      "tr": "然而，球员们从未放弃。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语",
      "d": "However 是副词作状语；gave up 意为“放弃”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/hrfLRMkmym6uevSZhJMxLS.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s13",
      "text": "They took every chance to learn and improve.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p2",
      "tr": "她们抓住每一个机会学习和提高。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "take every chance 意为“抓住每一个机会”；to learn... 是不定式作定语。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ybXA3eTQVcbUGTn3eMbaRB.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s14",
      "text": "For years, the team created many “firsts” in China’s sporting history.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p3",
      "tr": "多年来，这支球队在中国体育史上创造了许多“第一”。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "sporting history 意为“体育史”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/RYGgZbmkwojGyLsQDMHymE.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s15",
      "text": "People wondered about the key to their success.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p3",
      "tr": "人们想知道她们成功的关键。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "wondered about 意为“想知道”；key to... 意为“...的关键”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/Xi6akxwzZ3cZZoFviKvwBP.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s16",
      "text": "A team member explained it with just one simple sentence: “All of us love football and have the same goal.”",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p3",
      "tr": "一位队员用一句简单的话解释了这一点：“我们所有人都热爱足球，并且有着相同的目标。”",
      "g": "主从复合句",
      "d": "explained...with... 用...解释...；same goal 意为“相同的目标”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/mNybex3oH7Rea24u5WrS9W.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s17",
      "text": "Known as the Steel Roses of China, the team is close to many people’s hearts.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p4",
      "tr": "中国女足以“铿锵玫瑰”著称，深受许多人的喜爱。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 + 表语",
      "d": "Known as... 意为“以...著称”；close to one's heart 意为“深受某人喜爱”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/hAPHr227s8Ff4qccdJDUQJ.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s18",
      "text": "People love them for their courage and hard work.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p4",
      "tr": "人们因为她们的勇气和努力而爱她们。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 宾语",
      "d": "love sb. for sth. 因为某事而爱某人；courage 意为“勇气”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/QVKPCFzdERjjF9krdHTsmj.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s19",
      "text": "There are still many difficulties ahead.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p4",
      "tr": "前方仍有许多困难。",
      "g": "There be 存在句",
      "d": "difficulties ahead 意为“前方的困难”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/giLKnMbxcXtQGfWg9CGnSB.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u7-article-s20",
      "text": "But they will rise to every challenge, thanks to their shining spirit.",
      "paragraphId": "u7-article-p4",
      "tr": "但是凭借着她们昂扬闪耀的精神，她们定能直面所有挑战。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语",
      "d": "rise to the challenge 意为“迎接挑战”；thanks to 意为“由于/多亏”。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/8jv7ceuDndmpwiqssNdBoE.mp3"
    }
  ],
